br />\n相反後來台灣真係多得蔣介石唔少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75d95586077acfc9e558a8df302482470492da1c","tid":749434,"uid":32588,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"b9f75c845be426372dec597b49795ffc1f834b8b","tid":749434,"uid":135957,"like":2,"dislike":35,"score":-33,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T04:33:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T05:37:34.000Z","msg":"台灣繼續日治/自治可能仲好"},{"pid":"d59d78731856e2f2eb1b5d9f957d8627ee6283b5","tid":749434,"uid":99962,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T06:14:27.000Z","msg":"如果台灣有土改，有文革，有大躍進，有三反五反，用簡體字，由中共直接派書記管治，唔知會變成點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51b9bd6eb60ac1a7623aec538c1aabd1dfc9d93c","tid":749434,"uid":99962,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T06:17:32.000Z","msg":"其實蔡總統聽日宣布獨立，改國號為台灣國，申請加入聯合國，你估美國比唔比？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e4590261b17584a7ce64e393e3e3a8787da63ee","tid":749434,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51b9bd6eb60ac1a7623aec538c1aabd1dfc9d93c","tid":749434,"uid":99962,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T06:17:32.000Z","msg":"其實蔡總統聽日宣布獨立，改國號為台灣國，申請加入聯合國，你估美國比唔比？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T06:55:27.000Z","msg":"遲d美國廢埋UN後<br />\n仲入咩聯合國？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a5774eeec7d978eca9a014c9f45314bf518ba2d","tid":749434,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T07:07:09.000Z","msg":"潑漆青年反被潑漆！ 黑衣人朝青年頭頂狂噴「黃漆」<br />\n<br />\n獨派青年今年228至大溪慈湖陵寢潑漆，今天桃園地方法院第一次開庭，上午還至中正紀念堂潑紅漆，本預計10人到庭，2人遭警方逮捕，而開庭前更預計1點30分在法院前召開記者會，延後10分鐘記者會才剛開始，獨派青年郭潤庭才講沒幾句，一旁的羅宜馬上遭到黑<br />\n衣男「噴黃漆」，隨後現場青年和侵入2名男子打成一團，警方隨即逮捕隔離。<br />\n<br />\n桃園警分局表示，陳姓、胡姓等2名男子潛伏於民眾之間，伺機用噴漆向羅姓青年噴灑，警方立即逮捕隔離， 將以社會秩序維護法移請裁處，被害人若提出傷害或毀損告訴，本分局將依法偵辦。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/xMqvJlZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FxMqvJlZ.jpg&h=e7c1ecd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/AvlfYJq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FAvlfYJq.jpg&h=a7de92b1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/7321/3263475\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F7321%2F3263475&d=ZswPy%2BAChJBw01jT6W8w09ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=34b8fd0b\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/7321/3263475</a>"},{"pid":"f3537399992ad6ec9bbf4a7d96438f2f74e4f4ed","tid":749434,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T07:08:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/AvlfYJq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FAvlfYJq.jpg&h=a7de92b1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"88950c6a16528f29c6b71fb8d89b681dd16e4441","tid":749434,"uid":92178,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T07:10:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f6d49759287ae27f883646a5876319bf8ca2f521","tid":749434,"uid":92178,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T07:10:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bb98b842fbc2b22701a0760b31863bf1efb4a3f7","tid":749434,"uid":92178,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T07:10:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"53fad3e144b17f9ab7157f964815a3c237270f33","tid":749434,"uid":92178,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T07:11:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"98691d7788c66882edf80dd46aae284f20b33582","tid":749434,"uid":92178,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T07:11:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7fd0a5eb00eaea727829c5c26964a3f55ad049e3